## Prior Art Statement

To the best of the author's knowledge, no existing standard 
proposes:

- Magnetic ink as a carrier for AI-readable constitutional 
  payloads (distinct from magnetic stripe data encoding)
- A unified physical constitutional payload standard extending 
  the digital constitution protocol to physical objects
- The retrofit principle as a deployment strategy for 
  constituting the existing physical world

This document establishes the date of conception (2026-07-03) 
and sufficient technical detail to constitute prior art.

